AUDIO: 'insufficient for the establishment of a brand. You might be able to instantly identify the difference between concrete and dirt, but that recognition doesn\'t stir anything in you. You have no emotional response to it and it\'s entirely unlikely that it\'s going to influence you to purchase either of'

